skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: recipe idea
des:
Recipe Idea provides 3 recipe Ideas for an ingredient.
Alexa will say the name of the recipe and the accompanying cards will show you what website you can retrieve the recipes.

If it has no ideas for the ingredient this skill will tell you so.

Icons designed by Madebyoliver from Flaticon
Recipe Ideas powered by http://www.recipepuppy.com/
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
